Module org.cruk.clarity.api

Package org.cruk.clarity.api.impl

package org.cruk.clarity.api.impl
Concrete implementation classes of the Genologics API.
  • Related Packages
    Package
    Description
    org.cruk.clarity.api
    The main public package of the Genologics API.
    org.cruk.clarity.api.automation
    Tools to help move steps through Clarity using the API that allows processes to be run as if they are done through the browser, rather than the ExecutableProcess mechanism.
    org.cruk.clarity.api.cache
    Package supporting caching of Clarity entities in memory (or, if so configured, on disk) to reduce the amount of traffic being sent to and from the REST API.
    org.cruk.clarity.api.debugging
    Aspects and beans to aid with tracking the exchanges with the Genologics API for debugging purposes.
    org.cruk.clarity.api.http
    Classes specific to the REST template operation.
    org.cruk.clarity.api.jaxb
    Classes to aid the JAXB object mapping process.
